query:
INSERT INTO
    catch_areas (
    catch_area_id,longitude,latitude
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::INT[],$2::DECIMAL[],$3::DECIMAL[]
    )
        ON CONFLICT (catch_area_id) DO UPDATE SET longitude = COALESCE(catch_areas.longitude, EXCLUDED.longitude),latitude = COALESCE(catch_areas.latitude, EXCLUDED.latitude)
